#30000
Kombat Prep Room..(glow)..(hum)~

  As you glance around the Kombat Prep Room you notice all the
other fighters sharpening their blades and praying to their selected
gods. Now would be a good time for you to do the same because
stepping into the arena unprepared could be fatal.
  A small elderly man steps forward and speaks out to the group,

     "Shortly each of you will be positioned somewhere within
      the kombat arena. This will be your starting position from
      which you will proceed to hunt down and defeat all other
      fighters in the arena. The last remaining fighter will be
      our Mortal Kombat Champion."

  The old man then bows his head and is gone.
~
