#30036
Bozo's training room~
  You are standing in Bozo's training room.
This is the place where you gain levels and improve your stats!
To train for your next level, you type the following:

TRAIN LEVEL W (for warrior) or TRAIN LEVEL M (for mage), etc...
The word LEVEL will tell the trainer that you want to LEVEL, it does not
mean that you type in a number.  ie,  TRAIN 300 W (that's a NO NO!)

To improve your STATS, you do the following:
TRAIN STR (for Strength) or TRAIN INT (for Intelligence), etc...
It costs 4 practices to increase your main attribute and 6 for others.
~
